parameters: Noah's leg had deteriorated further than before, with the necrosis progressing.
Noah, whose life could end at any moment, was not a surprising sight...
That night, Luna and Noah talked in the park.

\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Luna, Becky, are you really going? Even Noah and Pole are coming along.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] I'll definitely defeat Lucia. That black witch.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] The "Knights of Messiah" from the Kingdom of Moduna didn't come to help us
though.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes, the "Knights of Messiah" from the Kingdom of Moduna on the surface.
They're a knightly order that helps other countries. I sent a letter asking for
support to their leader, Lord Ceres, but we were refused.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Can't be helped. The opponent is the direct-line mage Lucia. The power of a
direct-line mage is different from that of a normal mage, they possess an
incomparable amount of magical power.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] But we can't just let Lucia's tyranny continue any longer.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Geez, if the village chief's father heard about this, he'd be furious. Forming
a rebel army on your own and challenging the royal capital Jupiterino. There's
no way you can win against Lucia.

\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Big brother, keep it a secret from father, okay? We'll be the ones getting
scolded.
\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] But before you go, Luna, can I hear 'that answer'?

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] You see, I want Luna to be my girlfriend. I have many lovers... no, girlfriends
prepared by my father, but I prefer pure girls like Luna.

\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Geez... It's funny to hear playboy big brother talk about having a girlfriend.
You just want to make Luna another one of your sex friends, right?

\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Because your love arrows don't work on Luna, you're interested in her, right?
We brothers are the sons of the village chief, so most girls listen to what we
say, but Luna won't nod along.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] That's right. Luna has her childhood friend Noah after all. Luna, if you break
up with that poor Noah and become my girlfriend, you can indulge in as much
luxury as you want?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Dalieh, I'm sorry. To be honest, I don't find you attractive as a member of the
opposite sex...
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Dalieh, stop it! You're troubling Luna.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Noah, you're just a childhood friend of Luna's. It's cheeky for you to butt in
like this.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] No, I've been meaning to tell Dalieh directly for a while now. He's the son of
the village chief and he's been messing around with various girls, causing them
trouble. Now he's targeting Luna.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Let me make it clear, Dalieh. Both Luna and I dislike 'flashy men' like you!

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Sigh... It's pitiful for Luna to be with a poor man with no experience with
women like you.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Noah, just watch? I'll definitely make Luna my woman? I'll make her squeal with
my technique. All females are the same after all.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Too bad for you. Luna dislikes flashy men who make women cry like you do. Isn't
that right, Luna?

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Hmph... Luna, you'll understand soon enough. Who between Noah and me... is the
superior male?

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Sigh... Dalieh is the same as ever. He hits on any cute girl he sees. I'm glad
I got married to Pole early.

\C[20][Noah]\C[0] Heheh, I'm a lucky guy to have a cute woman like Becky as my wife. Right,
Becky? You love me, don't you?
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Pole, don't say embarrassing things in front of others.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Anyway, we're going to launch a surprise attack on the fortress in the imperial
capital Jupiterino and defeat Lucia. We can't stand Lucia's tyranny any longer.
Keep what happens from now on a secret from the village chief.
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Got it. Well, do your best out there.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Don't worry. If it gets dangerous, we'll escape. Well then... I'm off now.

Luna and the resistance head towards the fortress in the Jupiterino Kingdom.
There, Princess Lucia and the generals of the allied Valentia Kingdom had
gathered.
